OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774800665
OL,3,CWRU chair Richard Collier-Keywood to
OL,4,Cstep down
OL,6,FRichard Collier-Keywood will step down
OL,7,Fas chair of the Welsh Rugby Union at
OL,8,Fthe end of his three-year term in July.
OL,10,FThe WRU has confirmed Collier-Keywood
OL,11,Fwill not be seeking a second term in
OL,12,Fpost.
OL,14,FIn a statement Collier-Keywood said
OL,15,Fhis time in the position as been a
OL,16,F"tremendous privilege."
OL,18,F"My term as Chair comes to an end in
OL,19,FJuly 2026 and I have been reflecting
OL,20,Fwith the Board on what should happen
OL,21,Fnext.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774800665
OL,3,CWRU chair Richard Collier-Keywood to
OL,4,Cstep down
OL,6,F"We wanted to make this announcement
OL,7,Fto enable the recruitment process to
OL,8,Fstart and before the EGM is held on 13
OL,9,FApril 2026 so everyone goes into the
OL,10,FEGM process with the benefit of the
OL,11,Fsame knowledge.
OL,13,F"Over the course of the last few
OL,14,Fyears, the new Board has made key
OL,15,Fdecisions unanimously despite the very
OL,16,Fdifficult choices we have had to face.
OL,17,FI am fully committed to serving out
OL,18,Fthe remainder of my term, subject of
OL,19,Fcourse, to the outcome of the EGM."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
