PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774800665
OL,3,CWRU chair Richard Collier-Keywood to
OL,4,Cstep down
OL,6,FHe added: "The people I have had the
OL,7,Fpleasure of working with in the WRU
OL,8,Fand outside, and the importance of and
OL,9,Fpassion for rugby in Wales, have been
OL,10,Fa source of continued inspiration to
OL,11,Fme in carrying out this role.
OL,13,F"I am pleased to leave with two Welsh
OL,14,Fhead coaches in place with Steve Tandy
OL,15,Fand Sean Lynn and I am looking forward
OL,16,Fto watching from the terraces as our
OL,17,Fteams go from strength to strength."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/3
